---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
const pageTitle = "Portfolio | Home";
---

<Layout pageTitle={pageTitle}>
    <link
        rel="stylesheet"
        href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon@latest/devicon.min.css"
    />
    <div class="gif">
        <img width="300" height="259" alt="RaccoonSpaceGif" src="/space.webp" />
    </div>
    <h1>Abdullah Ahmed H</h1>
    <span class="badge">Aspiring Cybersecurity Professional</span>
    <h2>About</h2>
    <p>
        I’m a final-year Computer Science student with a strong curiosity. My
        journey started with a broad exploration of tech, but I’ve become
        increasingly passionate about cybersecurity, from web vulnerabilities to
        network security. As a quick learner, I’m always ready to take on new
        challenges, whether it's mastering a tool or solving difficult technical
        problems.
    </p>
    <p>
        With solid skills in Python and experience in full-stack development,
        I’m continuously refining my understanding of cybersecurity and web
        security analysis. I'm now seeking hands-on internship opportunities
        where I can apply my skills, contribute to meaningful projects, and make
        a tangible impact in the cybersecurity field.
    </p>
    <div class="center">
        <a href="/projects/">
            <button class="btn">My projects</button>
        </a>
    </div>
    <br />
    <div class="center">
        <a href="/achievements/">
            <button class="btn" style="--button:#D5B56E">My achievements</button
            >
        </a>
    </div>

    <h2>Skills</h2>
    <div class="skills center">
        <img
            class="skills__img"
            width="46"
            height="46"
            alt="Python"
            src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon@latest/icons/python/python-original.svg"
        />

        <img
            class="skills__img"
            width="46"
            height="46"
            alt="Linux"
            src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon@latest/icons/linux/linux-original.svg"
        />

        <img
            class="skills__img"
            width="46"
            height="46"
            alt="Django"
            src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon@latest/icons/django/django-plain.svg"
        />

        <img
            class="skills__img"
            width="46"
            height="46"
            alt="MySQL"
            src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon@latest/icons/mysql/mysql-original.svg"
        />

        <img
            class="skills__img"
            width="46"
            height="46"
            alt="C"
            src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon@latest/icons/c/c-original.svg"
        />

        <img
            class="skills__img"
            width="46"
            height="46"
            alt="Git"
            src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon@latest/icons/git/git-original.svg"
        />

        <img
            class="skills__img"
            width="46"
            height="46"
            alt="JavaScript"
            src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon@latest/icons/javascript/javascript-original.svg"
        />

        <img
            class="skills__img"
            width="46"
            height="46"
            alt="Angular JS"
            src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon@latest/icons/angularjs/angularjs-original.svg"
        />

        <img
            class="skills__img"
            width="46"
            height="46"
            alt="HTML"
            src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon@latest/icons/html5/html5-original.svg"
        />
    </div>

    <h2>Interests</h2>
    <p>
        Outside my interests in tech, you can find me reading fantasy novels or
        manga, among other interests like drawing and writing poems.
    </p>
</Layout>
